Spring Boot Service with Mysql to Login

Reference:
https://www.bezkoder.com/spring-boot-jwt-authentication/

https://github.com/bezkoder/spring-boot-spring-security-jwt-authentication

Dependency:
mysql

How to run local:
mvn spring-boot:run

Build jar
mvn spring-boot:build-image


